00:00:15.283 --> 00:00:19.068
So this is a sum from k
equals 1 to k equals 550,

00:00:19.068 --> 00:00:21.808
so we're going to have 550 terms here

00:00:21.808 --> 00:00:24.896
and it's the sum from k
equals 1 to k equals 550

00:00:24.896 --> 00:00:27.450
of 2k plus 50,

00:00:27.450 --> 00:00:29.238
so whenever I try to evaluate a series,

00:00:29.238 --> 00:00:31.397
I like to just expand
out the sum a little bit

00:00:31.397 --> 00:00:34.137
