feel for what it looks like,

00:00:34.137 --> 00:00:34.740
so let's see.

00:00:34.740 --> 00:00:35.948
This is going to look like,

00:00:35.948 --> 00:00:38.038
when k is equal 1, this is going to be

00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:40.894
