When k is equal to 2, it's going to be

00:00:42.589 --> 00:00:45.212
2 times 2 plus 50.

00:00:45.212 --> 00:00:46.652
When k is equal to 3, it's going to be

00:00:46.652 --> 00:00:49.485
2 times 3 plus 50.

00:00:49.485 --> 00:00:51.505
