going all the way until

00:00:51.505 --> 00:00:52.921
we get to the last term,

00:00:52.921 --> 00:00:55.266
when k is equal to 550, it's going to be

00:00:55.266 --> 00:00:59.654
2 times 550 plus 50.

00:00:59.654 --> 00:01:00.328
So let's see.

00:01:00.328 --> 00:01:01.744
This first term is going to be,

00:01:01.744 --> 00:01:05.761
