00:01:10.312 --> 00:01:12.146
plus the next term, 2 times 3 is 6

00:01:12.146 --> 00:01:14.352
plus 50 is 56,

00:01:14.352 --> 00:01:16.767
and we're going to go all the way,

00:01:16.767 --> 00:01:19.832
all the way to our last term,

00:01:19.832 --> 00:01:23.384
2 times 550 is 1100 plus 50

00:01:23.384 --> 00:01:25.776
is going to be 1150.

00:01:25.776 --> 00:01:27.749
So that gives us a good feel for this sum,

00:01:27.749 --> 00:01:28.492
for this series.

00:01:28.492 --> 00:01:31.256
We're going to start 52, and
we're just going to keep adding

00:01:31.256 --> 00:01:33.606
2 for each successive term, all the way

00:01:33.606 --> 00:01:35.185
until we get to 1150,

00:01:35.185 --> 00:01:38.320
and we're going to take
the sum of all of these,

00:01:38.320 --> 00:01:40.549
and since each successive
term, we're increasing

00:01:40.549 --> 00:01:41.663
