00:02:06.818 --> 00:02:10.232
thin air, so the formula for the sum

00:02:10.232 --> 00:02:12.855
of an arithmetic series,

00:02:12.855 --> 00:02:16.222
so the sum of the first
n terms is going to be

00:02:16.222 --> 00:02:20.634
